  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "chapterTitle": "四 变动之分析",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300095445_17_895-999",
          "range": "895-999",
          "rangeStart": 895,
          "rangeEnd": 999,
          "markText": "第二期是曹魏的上半期，在这一期的初年亦即黄初年间，魏吏部尚书制定了九品官人法，许多研究九品官人法的学者认为这是产生士族的最大原因，但是由于九品官人法以前士族已经出现，故九品官人法产生士族之说不能解释这种现象。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1753716232,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-28 23:23:52",
          "chapterUid": 17,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095445&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=895&rangeEnd=999",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a0320b0813ab8bc8g015a69?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=895&rangeEnd=999"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095445_32_15475-15560",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "15475-15560",
      "markText": "后期即黄皓当政至蜀亡，《三国志·蜀书》上共得四十七个官吏，其中十一人为由第一期任官而延续至第二期者，寒素占七人，嗣侯袭官者有十六人，另有十人亦可能以父为官，其他三人未详。",
      "totalCount": 537,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095445&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=15475&rangeEnd=15560",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a0320b0813ab8bc8g015a69?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=15475&rangeEnd=15560"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095445_31_5003-5025",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "5003-5025",
      "markText": "曹操之父是曹嵩，曹嵩之养父是汉桓帝宦官曹腾。",
      "totalCount": 528,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095445&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=5003&rangeEnd=5025",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a0320b0813ab8bc8g015a69?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=5003&rangeEnd=5025"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095445_45_3860-4113",
      "chapterUid": 45,
      "range": "3860-4113",
      "markText": "唐代官僚制度中的选制对地方人物具有巨大的吸引力，使郡姓大族疏离原籍、迁居两京，以便于投身官僚层；",
      "totalCount": 526,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095445&chapterUid=45&rangeStart=3860&rangeEnd=4113",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a0320b0813ab8bc8g015a69?chapterUid=45&rangeStart=3860&rangeEnd=4113"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095445_25_368-414",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "368-414",
      "markText": "综前所述，经两汉三百年渐次演变，暨政治力与社会势力相互融合，产生了一个新的社会阶层——士族；",
      "totalCount": 525,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095445&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=368&rangeEnd=414",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a0320b0813ab8bc8g015a69?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=368&rangeEnd=414"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095445_22_9120-9166",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "9120-9166",
      "markText": "其一，经济性：其社会地位的建立，起初在于获得比一般人多的财富，而从土地上获利是最普遍的现象。",
      "totalCount": 523,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095445&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=9120&rangeEnd=9166",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a0320b0813ab8bc8g015a69?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=9120&rangeEnd=9166"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095445_27_506-542",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "506-542",
      "markText": "颜之推初仕梁朝，任镇西府墨曹参军，经侯景之乱，又为梁散骑侍郎，奏舍人事。",
      "totalCount": 522,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095445&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=506&rangeEnd=542",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a0320b0813ab8bc8g015a69?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=506&rangeEnd=542"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095445_30_984-1064",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "984-1064",
      "markText": "后者社会成分的研究，系当政权业已建立，需要有庞大的官吏群为其推行政令，这一套架构中的每个官吏都足以影响政权的性质，量化官吏的社会成分，可以获得较清晰的社会轮廓。",
      "totalCount": 520,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095445&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=984&rangeEnd=1064",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a0320b0813ab8bc8g015a69?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=984&rangeEnd=1064"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095445_45_3652-3860",
      "chapterUid": 45,
      "range": "3652-3860",
      "markText": "士族是渐渐地新贯于中央，很少能以一道诏令立刻改变，任官中央而长期居留两京一带，有时候要经过数世才设籍并归葬于两京一带。",
      "totalCount": 519,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095445&chapterUid=45&rangeStart=3652&rangeEnd=3860",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2a0320b0813ab8bc8g015a69?chapterUid=45&rangeStart=3652&rangeEnd=3860"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095445_31_6502-6545",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "6502-6545",
      "markText": "在其屡踣屡起的记载中，发现每于败退势蹙之时，除曹氏宗族以外，他深得若干地方豪族的拥戴。",
